<para>Used by <ref refid="group__settings_1ga1dfe42f40a7d63bbdb81aed864d0ff12" kindref="member">settings_load_subtree_direct</ref> function.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">key</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
